{"tid":2031190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭定康：中國出現習獨裁 西方應覺醒「人民幣真香」完是幻象","createTime":"2020-05-23T08:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:50:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a02598b5c02ccc5cbc2806930324faf85d06d2cc","tid":2031190,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"彭定康斥中國出賣港人 籲西方停止向北京叩頭<br />\n23.05.2020 16:34<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康批評中國訂立香港國安法是出賣港人，認為西方應該停止為金錢向北京叩頭。彭定康接受《泰晤士報》訪問時說，中國出現新獨裁，西方不應被中方愚弄，以為叩頭就可以賺取大量金錢，完全是幻象，強調英國有道德、經濟及法律義務，支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289644&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289644%26csid%3D261_341&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=304d57a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289644&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3ad77d5e4012d4a6aacd5af9677a95bba8c1ca6f","tid":2031190,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3577c6d022a11b1b61a1b135e36304d4919022ca","tid":2031190,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"黎明？"},{"pid":"597c3bd45738e147864d0f6fe2eeb7f09ac62f10","tid":2031190,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"肥彭突然間咁清醒既"},{"pid":"0d0bcc6c6db965a86b29c0eb80892967ccc40833","tid":2031190,"uid":121146,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"彭定康比現今任何一個英國從政者都更清醒"},{"pid":"f8098480321a8e92e3a4825d86cb9ddfd89f58e9","